{"id":680943,"date":"2023-09-27T18:42:23","date_gmt":"2023-09-27T13:12:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/?p=680943"},"modified":"2025-09-03T15:34:15","modified_gmt":"2025-09-03T10:04:15","slug":"careers-after-online-ma-political-science","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/careers-after-online-ma-political-science","title":{"rendered":"Career opportunities after an online MA in Political Science"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Master of Arts (MA) in Political Science has gained significant popularity in recent years, especially with the emergence of online education platforms. This article delves into the various&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Political Science MA career prospects <\/strong>that await individuals who complete an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/master-of-arts-political-science\">online MA in Political Science <\/a>program. The MA graduates may be hired for managerial or executive positions or may work as social workers for NGOs. Job Security &#8211; Demand for political scientists is consistently high. There will be an even higher need as the need for public policy analysis grows in both the public and private sectors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-what-is-an-online-ma-in-political-science\"><strong>What is an online MA in Political Science?<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An online postgraduate degree program in political science will give students a thorough understanding of political systems, government, policy, and international relations. Students in this program analyze political ideas, research historical and current political concerns, and sharpen their critical thinking abilities.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Due to the flexibility of the online format, students can balance their education with other obligations. To give students a solid foundation in political studies, a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/master-of-arts-political-science\">Master of Arts in Political Science<\/a> online course aims to provide a thorough understanding of a wide range of political phenomena at the regional, national, and international levels and an in-depth analysis of these phenomena.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/regular-ma-vs-distance-ma-vs-online-ma\">Regular MA vs Distance MA vs Online MA<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Highlights:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Course Name<\/td><td>MA Political Science<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Full Form<\/td><td>Master of Arts in Political Science<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Duration<\/td><td>2 Years<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Basic Eligibility<\/td><td>Bachelor\u2019s degree with 50% or more in Political Science or in any other related field<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Examination Type<\/td><td>Semester<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Major Subjects<\/td><td>Political Theory, Public Administration, International Relations, Comparative Politics, and Public Laws. etc.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>MA Political Science Jobs<\/td><td>Academicians, Activists, Archivists and Political Content Writer, Political Consultant, etc<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Recruiting Areas<\/td><td>Universities, Administration, Campaigns, Political Houses, etc<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>MA Political Science Salary<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/www.payscale.com\/research\/IN\/Degree=Master_of_Arts_(MA)%2C_Political_Science_(PolySci)\/Salary\">INR 3,72,000<\/a><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-career-options-after-online-ma-in-political-science\"><strong>Career options after online MA in Political Science<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many career opportunities available for M.A. Political Science graduates, such as Public Administrator, Political Content Writer, Consultant, Subject Matter Expert, PR Executive, etc. Graduates of an online MA in Political Science have a wide array of career options to choose from. Some popular<strong> job roles for Political Science MAs<\/strong> and their respective salaries include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Political analyst<\/strong>: Political analysts examine political trends, policies, and events, providing insights to government agencies, media outlets, and research organizations. Salary range: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/political-research-analyst-salary\">INR 4 lakhs<\/a> per year.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Policy advisor<\/strong>: Policy advisors work with government bodies, non-profits, and think tanks to formulate and analyze policies. Salary range: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/policy-advisor-salary\">INR 2.4 lakhs<\/a> per year.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>International relations specialist<\/strong>: These specialists focus on global political dynamics, diplomacy, and international cooperation. They often work with foreign affairs departments, international organizations, or multinational corporations. Salary range: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/director-international-relations-salary\">INR 18.3 lakhs<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/collegedunia.com\/courses\/master-of-arts-ma-political-science\/career-options-and-jobs\"> <\/a>per year.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Public relations manager<\/strong>: Public relations managers handle communication between organizations and the public, including government agencies and political figures. Salary range:<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/pr-manager-salary\"> INR 7 lakhs<\/a> per year.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Political consultant<\/strong>: Political consultants offer strategic advice to political parties, candidates, and advocacy groups. Salary range: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/political-consultant-salary#:~:text=Political%20Consultant%20salary%20in%20India%20with%20less%20than%201%20year,based%20on%2087%20latest%20salaries.\">INR 3-13 lakhs<\/a> per year.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Read Here: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/master-of-arts-in-english-course-guide\">Master of Arts in English course guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-industries-where-ma-political-science-graduates-can-work\"><strong>Industries where MA Political Science graduates can work<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MA Political Science graduates can find employment in various industries, including:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Government Agencies<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Government Affairs Director<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Political Consultant<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Public Relations Specialist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Political Scientist<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Intelligence Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Policy Analyst<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>International Organizations<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Non-Governmental Organizations (NGOs)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Research Institutions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Media and Journalism<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Public Policy Think Tanks<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Academic Institutions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate Sector (Corporate Social Responsibility)<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out this blog on <a data-sider-select-id=\"a8dc88e3-349e-4ec0-a343-6c6491ef9307\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/lok-sabha-election-2024-a-guide-for-political-science-students\">lessons for political science students from Lok Sabha elections<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-benefits-of-pursuing-an-online-ma-in-political-science-program\"><strong>Benefits of pursuing an online MA in Political Science program<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MA graduates may be hired for managerial or executive positions or may work as social workers for NGOs. Demand for political scientists is consistently high. There will be an even higher need as the need for public policy analysis grows in both the public and private sectors. There are various online Political Science MA benefits, such as:&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Flexibility<\/strong>: Online programs allow learners to study at their own pace, making balancing education with work or other commitments easier.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Diverse learning environment<\/strong>: Interacting with peers from various locations provides a diverse perspective on political issues and global affairs.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Access to resources<\/strong>: Online platforms often provide access to vast digital libraries, research materials, and recorded lectures.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Enhanced communication skills<\/strong>: Online discussions and virtual interactions improve written communication skills, which are vital for various job roles.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Career advancement<\/strong>: An MA degree can open doors to higher-paying positions and leadership roles within organizations.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/career-options-for-ma-sociology-graduates\">Career options for Master of Arts in Sociology graduates<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-skills-you-will-earn-from-an-online-ma-in-political-science\"><strong>Skills you will earn from an Online MA in Political Science<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You will develop the writing, analytical, communication, and data skills that are essential for a successful career as a political science student. You can think critically and creatively, thanks to it. <strong>Political Science graduates in India <\/strong>improve their analytical skills by being able to evaluate statistical arguments. Students who enroll in an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/master-of-arts-political-science\">online MA in Political Science<\/a> program get valuable skills such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Critical thinking<\/strong>: Analyzing political situations and proposing effective solutions.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Research abilities<\/strong>: Conducting in-depth research using various sources and methodologies.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Communication proficiency<\/strong>: Effectively articulating complex ideas both in writing and verbal communication.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Data interpretation<\/strong>: Interpreting political data, trends, and statistics to support decision-making.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Problem-solving<\/strong>: Developing strategies to address political challenges and conflicts.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Read More:<a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/best-marketing-jobs-in-india\"> Best marketing jobs &amp; careers to pursue in 2023<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Grow with an online MA in Political Science from SMU<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Completing an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/master-of-arts-political-science\">online MA in Political Science<\/a> from Sikkim Manipal University opens up diverse career pathways and personal and professional growth opportunities. Graduates with a strong background in political analysis can help shape policies, advance international relations, and make wise political choices. Study and upskill seamlessly by attending live and recorded lectures and writing online proctored exams while continuing to work.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read More:<a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/career-options-after-ma-in-english\"> Career Opportunities after a Master of Arts in English<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Conclusion<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The increasing popularity of earning an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/master-of-arts-political-science\">online MA in Political Science<\/a> in India shows how crucial political knowledge is becoming in various fields. Graduates of this program carry with them a plethora of information and abilities that can greatly influence political discourse, policy-making, and international relations when they enter the working world. Whether in the government, non-profit, or corporate sector, the career opportunities for MA in Political Science graduates in India are both diverse and promising. Shape your career effectively with this knowledge of Political Science research and careers.&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Master of Arts (MA) in Political Science has gained significant popularity in recent years, especially with the emergence of online education platforms. This article delves into the various&nbsp; Political Science MA career prospects that await individuals who complete an online MA in Political Science program. The MA graduates may be hired for managerial or executive [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":19,"featured_media":679850,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[610],"tags":[19,231],"class_list":["post-680943","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-master-of-arts","tag-online-degree","tag-online-ma-in-political-science"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>Career opportunities after an online MA in Political Science - Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Looking to pursue an online master&#039;s degree in political science? Here are the top jobs you can explore after an online MA.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/680943\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Career opportunities after an online MA in Political Science - Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Looking to pursue an online master&#039;s degree in political science? Here are the top jobs you can explore after an online MA.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/careers-after-online-ma-political-science\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2023-09-27T13:12:23+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2025-09-03T10:04:15+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/MA-Political-Science-SMU-1.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"400\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"170\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Editorial Team\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twitter:label1\" content=\"Written by\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data1\" content=\"Editorial Team\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:label2\" content=\"Estimated reading time\" \/>\n\t<meta name=\"twitter:data2\" content=\"5 minutes\" \/>\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\" class=\"yoast-schema-graph\">{\"@context\":\"https:\\\/\\\/schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/blogs\\\/careers-after-online-ma-political-science\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/blogs\\\/careers-after-online-ma-political-science\",\"name\":\"Career opportunities after an online MA in Political Science - Online Manipal\",\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/#website\"},\"primaryImageOfPage\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/blogs\\\/careers-after-online-ma-political-science#primaryimage\"},\"image\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipal.com\\\/blogs\\\/careers-after-online-ma-political-science#primaryim